&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stratolaunch is a technology accelerator that engineers operationally realistic testing at Mach 5+. Our air-launched, Talon testbeds are reusable, cost-effective platforms that enable routine access to the hypersonic environment. We deliver flight data critical to validating system performance and achieving rapid technology deployment. Together with our customers, we drive innovations that are imperative to advancing national security.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A&amp;amp;P License Required &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
