&lt;li&gt;Experience integrating launch vehicle or aircraft electrical power systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with troubleshooting Ethernet networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with data acquisition and instrumentation (thermocouples, accelerometers, strain)&lt;/li&gt;
