&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stratolaunch is a technology accelerator that engineers operationally realistic testing at Mach 5+. Our air-launched, Talon testbeds are reusable, cost-effective platforms that enable routine access to the hypersonic environment. We deliver flight data critical to validating system performance and achieving rapid technology deployment. Together with our customers, we drive innovations that are imperative to advancing national security.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Executive Assistant &lt;/strong&gt;provides comprehensive administrative and clerical support to the CEO and COO, serving as a key liaison between executives and the Board of Managers/Advisors. This highly visible role requires exceptional professionalism, discretion, and judgment. The Executive Assistant will coordinate complex schedules, arrange meetings, handle sensitive information, manage travel logistics, and oversee a variety of administrative tasks to ensure the seamless operation of the executive office.&lt;/p&gt;
